OL,3,CTeenager arrested after young boy
OL,4,Cseriously injured in hit-and-run
OL,6,FA teenager has been arrested after a
OL,7,Fyoung boy was seriously injured when a
OL,8,Fcar collided with a bike in Birmingham
OL,9,Fyesterday evening.
OL,11,FPolice were called to St Andrews Road,
OL,12,FNechells, at 8.40pm on Friday 3rd
OL,13,FApril to reports that a 13-year-old
OL,14,Fboy had been seriously injured.
OL,16,FThe driver of the vehicle had also
OL,17,Ffled the scene.
OL,19,FThe boy was taken to hospital with
OL,20,Fsuspected life-threatening injuries
OL,21,Fand remains in a serious condition.
