OL,3,CTeenager arrested after young boy
OL,4,Cseriously injured in hit-and-run
OL,6,FA 19-year-old was arrested shortly
OL,7,Fafter the incident, on suspicion of
OL,8,Fcausing serious injury by dangerous
OL,9,Fdriving and remains in custody.
OL,11,FPolice are asking anyone with dashcam
OL,12,For CCTV footage to contact them.
